  {title: "Between the Lines Mural Art by Cyrcle", author: "Léa", link: "http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/15/between-the-lines-mural-art-by-cyrcle/", content: "<p>Le duo composé des deux artistes américains David Leavitt et David Torres et regroupés sous le nom de <a href=\"http://www.cyrcle.com/\">CYRCLE</a>, a réalisé une nouvelle oeuvre de street-art à Manille, au Philippines, intitulée <em>Between the Lines</em>. Elle est représentée par un astronaute en noir et blanc et mis en scène avec des lignes verticales lui offrant un aspect en relief.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/15/between-the-lines-mural-art-by-cyrcle/betweenthelines1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-719564\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/betweenthelines1-900x591.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"591\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/15/between-the-lines-mural-art-by-cyrcle/betweenthelines2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-719579\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/betweenthelines2-900x600.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/15/between-the-lines-mural-art-by-cyrcle/betweenthelines3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-719568\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/betweenthelines3-900x600.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/15/between-the-lines-mural-art-by-cyrcle/betweenthelines4/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-719569\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/betweenthelines4-900x600.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/15/between-the-lines-mural-art-by-cyrcle/betweenthelines5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-719570\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/betweenthelines5-900x600.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/15/between-the-lines-mural-art-by-