  {title: "Cute Macarons inspired by Emojis and Studio Ghibli Characters", author: "Daniella", link: "http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/16/cute-macarons-inspired-by-emojis-and-studio-ghibli-characters/", content: "<p>Basé en Californie, le duo de pâtissiers de <a href=\"https://instagram.com/honeyandbutter/\">Honey &amp; Butter</a> confectionne d’adorables petits macarons prenant la forme de personnages issus de la pop culture, des animations Ghibli, de Disney ou faisant référence aux Emojis. Une sélection de leurs jolies créations est à découvrir en images. </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/16/cute-macarons-inspired-by-emojis-and-studio-ghibli-characters/macaron-0/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-719992\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/macaron-0.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/16/cute-macarons-inspired-by-emojis-and-studio-ghibli-characters/macaron-1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-719993\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/macaron-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"676\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/16/cute-macarons-inspired-by-emojis-and-studio-ghibli-characters/macaron-3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-719994\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/macaron-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"676\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/16/cute-macarons-inspired-by-emojis-and-studio-ghibli-characters/macaron-4/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-719995\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/macaron-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"681\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/16/cute-macarons-inspired-by-emojis-and-studio-ghibli-characters/macaron-5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-719996\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/macaron-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"889\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/16