  {title: "500px NEXT: Let’s Go Exploring with Rob Sese", author: "DL Cade", link: "https://iso.500px.com/500px-next-lets-go-exploring-with-rob-sese/", content: "<p><i><b>Editor’s Note</b>: <a href=\"https://iso.500px.com/category/creative/special-features/500px-next/\"><u>500px NEXT</u></a> is a new <a href=\"https://iso.500px.com/category/creative/special-features/\"><u>Special Feature</u></a> we’re debuting here on 500px ISO. NEXT stands for Noteworthy, Emerging, eXpressive, and Tenacious: the four characteristics that every artist labeled a “500px NEXT” photographer has in spades.</i></p>\n<p>Their work inspires, pushes boundaries, and sits at the bleeding edge of photography’s latest trends and techniques. If you think you deserve to be featured as a 500px NEXT photographer, or you know someone who does, <a href=\"mailto:dl@500px.com\"><u>send me an email at dl@500px.com</u></a>.</p>\n<hr>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/119864547/m%3D900/542ea6f4cafaf2e6981c85c4c24967bd\" alt=\"Vernal Fall by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/119864547/vernal-fall-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Vernal Fall by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Of the newer faces that have started using <a href=\"https://500px.com\">500px</a> actively over the past few months, very few have taken off as well as Chicago-based Travel and Lifestyle photographer <a href=\"https://500px.com/robsese\"><b><u>Rob Sese</u></b></a>. A Guest Editor <a href=\"https://iso.500px.com/ec-october-2015/\">this month</a> <i>and</i> the winner of <a href=\"https://iso.500px.com/check-out-the-winners-of-our-photos-of-photogs-quest/\">our Photographing Photographers Photo Quest</a>, he’s amassed over 2,500 followers and nearly 600K photo views, almost all of them coming after he got active on the site again on August 29th of this year!</p>\n<p>It would be easy to pass this off as luck, but the reality is that skill, a beautiful eye, and his knack for mixing a human touch into his landscapes has a lot more to do with it.</p>\n<p>A distant person, long lonely road, or even just the ripples from a stone thrown into a pond all indicate that this isn’t a static scene in nature—humanity was here, these elements imply, and thanks to them we’re able to place ourselves within the context of his images.</p>\n<p>Looking through his portfolio, you feel as if you’re out there with him, exploring the natural wonders that call our name from time to time.</p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/124502963/m%3D900/d08af0e14ed6d53e0e7c4fc5239a7b13\" alt=\"Autumn in the Tetons by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/124502963/autumn-in-the-tetons-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Autumn in the Tetons by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/121972817/m%3D900/ee28ad617285379dbce9f7f52141b5a0\" alt=\"Norwegian Heights by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/121972817/norwegian-heights-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Norwegian Heights by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/121488495/m%3D900/5f37f729ca65c700b89669d535877176\" alt=\"Foggy sunrise in Olden, Norway by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/121488495/foggy-sunrise-in-olden-norway-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Foggy sunrise in Olden, Norway by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/120930995/m%3D900/793016033ba32732af499bc5a522221b\" alt=\"Mt. Rainier National Park by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/120930995/mt-rainier-national-park-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Mt. Rainier National Park by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/123911703/m%3D900/d66252d30d80f8dfd780c4fae80aee74\" alt=\"Dylan by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/123911703/dylan-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Dylan by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/121706891/m%3D900/a3fdddf33517858c334035077d84cb58\" alt=\"Olden, Norway by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/121706891/olden-norway-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Olden, Norway by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/119929663/m%3D900/1f4b324c3be2bb06ca9e33fba59ac812\" alt=\"Oregon by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/119929663/oregon-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Oregon by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/119864235/m%3D900/b2895aae6977fd21a0bc08d799c06219\" alt=\"Yosemite by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/119864235/yosemite-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Yosemite by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/125027421/m%3D900/59dcfdcde853f44093f13491af066cf7\" alt=\"Norge by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/125027421/norge-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Norge by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/122770841/m%3D900/1ac010c5c4e8ea72f8c0a5aa6a43b5bf\" alt=\"The off beaten path... by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/122770841/the-off-beaten-path-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"The off beaten path... by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/119865783/m%3D900/a7b1e173a7b2d57a6098cb1905cf368d\" alt=\"Jillian by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/119865783/jillian-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Jillian by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/124229921/m%3D900/45e0848cf5c65f3e48a706f38951131c\" alt=\"Hints of Autumn in Norway by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/124229921/hints-of-autumn-in-norway-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Hints of Autumn in Norway by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/121403005/m%3D900/eb4b0125b7ecb1271726ca1b26837772\" alt=\"Låtefossen, Norway by Rob Sese on 500px.com\">\n  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://500px.com/photo/121403005/l%C3%A5tefossen-norway-by-rob-sese\" alt=\"Låtefossen, Norway by Rob Sese on 500px.com\"></a>\n</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Rob doesn’t just take pictures out in nature, his photos of the urban landscape of Chicago are equally compelling, just not what we wanted to feature here. To see more of his work (and you definitely should) give him a follow <a href=\"https://500px.com/robsese\"><b><u>on 500px</u></b></a>, visit <a href=\"http://www.robsese.com/\"><b><u>his website</u></b></a>, or check him out on <a href=\"https://instagram.com/rob.sese/\"><b><u>Instagram</u></b></a>, <a href=\"http://robsesphoto.tumblr.com/\"><b><u>Tumblr</u></b></a>, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/robsesphoto\"><b><u>Twitter</u></b></a>.</p>", publishedDate: "2015-10-16", contentSnippet: "Explore nature's beauty with Rob Sese, one of the most compelling photographers to recently return to the 500px community.", feed_id: 2, categories: "[\"500px NEXT\", \"Headline\", \"Inspiration\", \"Special Features\", \"Spotlights\", \"500pxnext\", \"artist spotlight\", \"landscape photography\", \"natural\", \"nature\", \"Photography Spotlight\", \"Rob Sese\", \"spotlight\", \"travel\", \"travel photography\"]"},
  {title: "Glass Wave Sculptures", author: "Léa", link: "http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/glass-wave-sculptures/", content: "<p>L’artiste écossais <a href=\"http://grahammuir.co.uk/\">Graham Muir</a> imagine des sculptures de verre colorées, prenant la forme de vagues. Ses créations sont élaborées à partir de larges sphères en verre soufflée, sculptées pour en constituer les pièces finales. Ces vagues semblent être comme figées par le gel.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/glass-wave-sculptures/glasswave1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720234\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/glasswave1-900x545.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"545\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/glass-wave-sculptures/glasswave2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720260\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/glasswave2-900x888.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"888\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/glass-wave-sculptures/glasswave3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720261\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/glasswave3-900x851.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"851\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/glass-wave-sculptures/glasswave4/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720237\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/glasswave4-900x612.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"612\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/glass-wave-sculptures/glasswave5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720238\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/glasswave5-900x795.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"795\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/glass-wave-sculptures/glasswave6/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720239\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/glasswave6-900x756.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"756\"></a></p>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/glass-wave-sculptures/glasswave3