  {title: "Smoky Double Exposure Animals Illustrations", author: "Donnia", link: "http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/smoky-double-exposure-animals-illustrations/", content: "<p><a href=\"https://instagram.com/mrtaylordani/\">Taylor Dániel</a> est un artiste basé à Budapest, qui dessine d’incroyables portraits d’animaux en double exposition. Il utilise une technique mixte, combinant photographie et illustration. Il a recours à un effect de « fumée » pour ajouter une dimension surréaliste. Ses oeuvres sont disponibles sur son <a href=\"https://society6.com/taylordaniel\">shop</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/smoky-double-exposure-animals-illustrations/danieltaylor-1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720017\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/danieltaylor-1-900x898.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"898\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/smoky-double-exposure-animals-illustrations/danieltaylor-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720018\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/danieltaylor-2-900x898.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"898\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/smoky-double-exposure-animals-illustrations/danieltaylor-3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720019\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/danieltaylor-3-900x903.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"903\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/smoky-double-exposure-animals-illustrations/danieltaylor-4/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720020\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/danieltaylor-4-900x897.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"897\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/19/smoky-double-exposure-animals-illustrations/danieltaylor-5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720021\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/danieltaylor-5-900x900.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://ww