  {title: "Drawing Streets on Paper Coffee Cups", author: "Léa", link: "http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/drawing-streets-on-paper-coffee-cups/", content: "<p><a href=\"http://www.mariyasketch.com/home/\">Mariya Suzuki</a> est une illustratrice basée à Tokyo. Elle a choisi d’ajouter une touche de couleurs et de fantaisie aux goblets de café cartonnés à emporter qu’elle trouvait trop simples. Ses inspirations sont constituées par les rues dans lesquelles elle se trouve, les bars, les magasins, les rames de métro ou encore les personnes qu’elle est amenée à croiser. </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/drawing-streets-on-paper-coffee-cups/streetscoffeecup1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720572\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/streetscoffeecup1-900x404.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"404\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/drawing-streets-on-paper-coffee-cups/streetscoffeecup2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720573\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/streetscoffeecup2-900x404.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"404\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/drawing-streets-on-paper-coffee-cups/streetscoffeecup3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720574\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/streetscoffeecup3-900x404.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"404\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/drawing-streets-on-paper-coffee-cups/streetscoffeecup4/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720575\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/streetscoffeecup4-900x404.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"404\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/drawing-streets-on-paper-coffee-cups/streetscoffeecup5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720576\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/streetscoffeecup5-900x404.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"404\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/1