  {title: "Scenes from the Past juxtaposed with Present", author: "Daniella", link: "http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/scenes-from-the-past-juxtaposed-with-present/", content: "<p>Rédacteur du Magazine <a href=\"http://www.esquire.com/\">Esquire</a>, <a href=\"https://instagram.com/nicksullivanesq/\">Nick Sullivan</a> combine des scènes du passé avec le moment présent en juxtaposant des photos prises dans les rues de Londres, New-York et Paris il y a plusieurs années sur l’exact même endroit aujourd’hui. Les images qu’il choisit de juxtaposer rendent son projet d’autant plus fascinant qu’elles représentent des portraits de musiciens ou d’acteurs célèbres tels que Bob Dylan, les Rolling Stones ou encore Alain Delon.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/scenes-from-the-past-juxtaposed-with-present/double1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720695\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Double1-900x900.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/scenes-from-the-past-juxtaposed-with-present/double2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720696\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Double2-900x900.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/scenes-from-the-past-juxtaposed-with-present/double3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720697\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Double3-900x900.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/scenes-from-the-past-juxtaposed-with-present/double4/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720698\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Double4-900x900.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/scenes-from-the-past-juxtaposed-with-present/double5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720699\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Double5-900x900.jpeg\" 