  {title: "Giant Animals in Cityscapes Paintings", author: "Daniella", link: "http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/giant-animals-in-cityscapes-paintings/", content: "<p><em>Searching for Paradise</em> est une série de peintures réalisée par l’artiste japonais <a href=\"http://nakanoshuichi.com/\">Shuichi Nakano</a>. Ses toiles à l’aspect surréaliste mettent en scène dans un monde qui s’apparente au notre, des hordes d’animaux géants surplombant le paysage urbain, comme un constat dramatique qui illustre l’invasion progressive des hommes sur leur habitat naturel.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/giant-animals-in-cityscapes-paintings/nakano-0/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720841\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/nakano-0-900x695.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"695\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/giant-animals-in-cityscapes-paintings/nakano-1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720842\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/nakano-1-900x754.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"754\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/giant-animals-in-cityscapes-paintings/nakano-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720843\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/nakano-2-900x1087.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"1087\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/giant-animals-in-cityscapes-paintings/nakano-3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720844\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/nakano-3-900x1120.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"1120\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/giant-animals-in-cityscapes-paintings/nakano-4/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720845\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/nakano-4-900x723.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"723\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/20/giant-animals-in-cityscapes-paintings/nakano-5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720846\"><img src=