  {title: "Abstract Textures Photography", author: "Daniella", link: "http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/", content: "<p>L’artiste <a href=\"http://www.benjaminhenon.com/\">Benjamin Henon</a> que nous avons déjà présenté avec sa série originale de plats revisités a réalisé une série de visuels représentant des textures liquides et aériennes tels que des nuages de fumée compacte, de l’essence en ébullition et une bulle d’eau flottant dans les airs.  </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/en/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-0/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720857\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-0-900x711.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"711\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/en/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720858\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-1-900x710.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"710\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/en/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720859\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-3-900x709.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"709\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/en/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-4/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720860\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-4-900x724.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"724\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/en/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720861\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-5-900x699.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"699\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/en/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-6/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720862\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-6-900x709.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"709\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/en/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-7/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720863\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"641\" height=\"810\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/en/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-8/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720864\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"642\" height=\"810\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/en/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-9/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720865\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-9-900x643.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"643\"></a></p>\n\n\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-9/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-9-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"henon-9\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-8/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-8-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"henon-8\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-7/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-7-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"henon-7\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-6/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-6-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"henon-6\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-5/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon-5-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"henon-5\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/abstract-textures-photography/henon-4/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/henon