  {title: "Port Louis Brand Identity by Vallée Duhamel", author: "Donnia", link: "http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/", content: "<p>Le studio <a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/tag/vallee-duhamel/\">Vallée Duhamel</a> (composé d’Eve Duhamel et de Julien Vallée) s’est occupé de l’identité de la marque de bijoux canadienne Port Louis. Ils ont imaginé une série de photos, dont quelques unes en diptyques, et des cartes de visite qui illustrent l’univers et les couleurs de cette joaillerie éthique.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/port-louis-dyptique-1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720795\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Port-Louis-dyptique-1-900x450.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"450\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/port-louis-dyptique-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720796\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Port-Louis-dyptique-2-900x450.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"450\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/port-louis-home-1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720797\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Port-Louis-home-1-900x399.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"399\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/port-louis-home-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720798\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Port-Louis-home-2-900x399.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"399\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/portlouis5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720799\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/portlouis5-900x450.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"450\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/portlouis6/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-720800\"><img src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/portlouis6-900x450.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"450\"></a></p>\n\n<p><strong>Credits :</strong> </p>\n<p><em>Producer: Inès Steinmetzer.<br>\nCoordinator: Faye Duhamel.<br>\nDP: Yann Jobin.<br>\nPhotograph’s assistant: Jérôme Bertrand.<br>\nArt Director: Gabrielle Matte.<br>\nIntern: Camille Marteil.<br>\nStylist: Sarah Laroche.<br>\nHair/Makeup Artist: Léonie Lévesque.<br>\nModel #1 Camille – Agence Folio.<br>\nModel #2 Charlene – Agence Montage.</em><br>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/portlouis6/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/portlouis6-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"portlouis6\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/portlouis5/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/portlouis5-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"portlouis5\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/port-louis-home-2/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Port-Louis-home-2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Port-Louis-home-2\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/port-louis-home-1/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Port-Louis-home-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Port-Louis-home-1\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/port-louis-dyptique-2/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Port-Louis-dyptique-2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Port-Louis-dyptique-2\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.fubiz.net/2015/10/21/port-louis-brand-identity-by-vallee-duhamel/port-louis-dyptique-1/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.fubiz.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Port-Louis-dyptique-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Port-Louis-dyptique-1\"></a>\n</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/fubiz/~4/NwNKwi5b1v0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\">", publishedDate: "2015-10-21", contentSnippet: "Le studio Vallée Duhamel (composé d&#8217;Eve Duhamel et de Julien Vallée) s&#8217;est occupé de l&#8217;identité de la marque ...", feed_id: 1, categories: "[\"Design\", \"Fashion\", \"Photography\", \"Print\", \"Product\", \"brand\", \"branding\", \"Business Cards\", \"cards\", \"diptych\", \"eve duhamel\", \"Identity\", \"jewel\", \"jewellery\", \"julien vallée\", \"port louis\", \"vallée duhamel\", \"visual\"]"}
